title: Kaduva
subTitle: Kaduva pledges to seek revenge against IG Joseph when the police officer sends Kaduva to jail and torments his loved ones.

title: I Love You
subTitle: Santosh, a carefree youth, parts ways with his lover, Dharmika, during his college days. Years later, after his marriage to Gowri, he runs into her, which leaves him in a dilemma.

title: One Way Ticket
subTitle: Kunjappu, a jeep driver and an ardent admirer of superstar Mammootty, finds himself troubled when his relationship is in disarray. But he is rapt when Mammootty himself intervenes to solve his issues.

title: Wagah
subTitle: An Indian soldier falls in love with a Muslim girl near the India-Pakistan border. However, when a riot breaks out in the area, the man finds his love and his life at risk.

title: Veera Sivaji

subTitle: When mysterious deaths plague a haunted bungalow, a young man begins to investigate. However, his research leads him to uncover the mansion's dark past and ghostly secrets.

title: Dasara
subTitle: In a town that is dependent on coal mining, the lives of three childhood friends turn chaotic when they get into a fight with the son of the village headman.

subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Sangathamizhan
subTitle: Murugan, a happy-go-lucky young man, falls in love with the daughter of Sanjay, an industrialist. However, trouble arises when Sanjay notices that Murugan looks like a figure from his dark past.

title: Guardian
subTitle: An unavenged woman returns from the dead to terrify and terrorise those who tormented her when she was alive.

subTitle: Two penniless friends are in desperate need of money in order to marry their respective girlfriends. In their attempts to make quick money, they kidnap a rich woman's pet and demand a hefty ransom.

subTitle: Following a tycoon's discovery of a rare oil reserve, a compassionate beggar gets trapped in the dangerous mechanisms of his rapacious scheme.
